originalText.text: When I started looking into getting a prenup done I was shocked by cost I was getting quoted by attorneys to put together a relatively basic document. When I saw the price for JustLaw to do the same thing was only a fraction of the cost, I was apprehensive (if it sounds too good to be true...) but decided to move forward. Now that everything is all completed, I'm so glad I did! Angelina was very responsive and the whole process was simple and easy. I would definitely recommend them to anyone who wants the piece of mind of having a prenup without the excessive costs.
